---
title: SpacesSync — C4 Level 1 (System Context)
---
flowchart TB
    classDef person fill:#08427b,stroke:#0a5394,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef system fill:#1168bd,stroke:#0e5aa7,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef external fill:#999,stroke:#666,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef config fill:#5a4a1e,stroke:#d4a853,color:#fff,stroke-width:1.5px

    User([User<br/><br/>Mac user with multiple<br/>monitors and Spaces]):::person

    subgraph Scope [SpacesSync — scope of this project]
        Spoon[SpacesSync.spoon<br/><br/>Lua module loaded by Hammerspoon.<br/>Watches Space changes and<br/>mirrors them across a sync group.]:::system
    end

    Init[~/.hammerspoon/init.lua<br/><br/>User config: syncGroups, hotkeys.<br/>Calls hs.loadSpoon SpacesSync<br/>and :start.]:::config
    HS[Hammerspoon<br/><br/>macOS automation runtime.<br/>Provides hs.spaces, hs.screen,<br/>hs.canvas, hs.timer, hs.settings.]:::external
    OS[macOS Window Server<br/>+ Mission Control<br/><br/>Authoritative source of<br/>Spaces state. Driven via<br/>private CGSSpace APIs.]:::external
    Plist[hs.settings store<br/><br/>org.hammerspoon.Hammerspoon.plist<br/>persists workspace names<br/>across restarts.]:::external

    User -->|switches Space via<br/>Mission Control,<br/>Ctrl+Arrow,<br/>or hotkey| OS
    User -->|edits config| Init
    User -->|presses bound<br/>hotkeys ⌃⌥⌘Y/N/R| Spoon

    Init -->|loads + configures| Spoon
    Spoon -->|hosted by,<br/>uses Lua APIs of| HS
    HS -->|observes + drives<br/>via private APIs| OS
    Spoon -->|reads + writes<br/>workspace names| Plist
    Spoon -->|shows popup,<br/>picker, status HUD<br/>via hs.canvas| User

    %% Layout hint
    User ~~~ Init
